spx.av

Class VideoStandard

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.av.VideoStandard

  • public class VideoStandard
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains constants that match the enumeration values of the SPxAVAnalogVideoStandard enum from SPxAVCommon.h and functions to convert a video standard constant to a string.
